snippet.title: Nick Reckless in The Curse of the Lost Cause (Teaser)
snippet.description:
A terrible curse fell on our hero.
To get rid of it, he must put some things back to their place.
Our hero will have to overcome the obstacles that stand in his way.
But will the curse give him the chance to achieve his goals?

-Pre alpha footage -
